---
title: Cajun Ranch Chicken Salad with Tomato & Shredded Carrots
description: Running out of lunch ideas? Fallen into a salad rut? It's not so easy to come up with a hearty, fresh, filling, yet light and satisfying option. But our chefs are always thinking: They’ve set you up today with fully cooked chicken breast, and all that’s left to do is chop the lettuce and tomato, combine the ranch dressing with the creamy, savory Cajun additions, plus carrot, and boom!—a tasty lunch in minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cajun-ranch-chicken-salad-748aff8d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cajun-ranch-chicken-salad-638fa5df02475cb47e07295a-b715ee03.pdf
time required: 10 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 440 kcal
  fat: 28 g
  saturated fat: 5 g
  carbohydrates: 18 g
  sugar: 9 g
  protein: 31 g
  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 920 mg
course: main course
